Using this repo
===============

Install Oracle’s VirtualBox 

  http://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads

Install Vagrant (packages for Windows, Mac, Linux) 

  http://downloads.vagrantup.com

Install Git if you don't already have it.

Linux and Mac OS X:

  $ git clone <GIT_URL>
  $ cd funeralweb
  $ git pull && git submodule init && git submodule update && git submodule status
  $ vagrant up

Windows:

  1. Clone <GIT_URL>
  2. Right click on funeralweb folder and select Git Submodule update
  3. Open up Command prompt and run "vagrant up" in your funeral_stationery directory!

Your site is ready to use here:

  http://localhost:8999/

Using Vagrant
=============

To start your vm

  vagrant up

To stop your VM

  vagrant halt

To delete your VM

  vagrant destroy

To re-provision your VM

  vagrant provision
